        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Something no one has mentioned is using shadow step when dueling a melee. It can keep you from getting hit at all. Screaming terror can give you time to land your dots too. Also nullify magic to strip off those buffs, oh yeah and throw all your best buffs on, even the one that takes the peridot.  =)</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
