        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I only speak from the 50+ duelling:</P><P>ALWAYS duel outdoors... DL portal area is a good way, because much hills and no Mobs at all.</P><P>Bury your levitate and you win against all melees who do not have instacast dispells.</P><P>Against a wizzie with Epic get your resists up... a lvl 60 wizzie with decent resists and epic and manaburn is unbeatable.</P><P>Bards unbeatable because of speed... they run away, hide and come back.</P><P>Against enchanters you need mr of 180 and he has NO chance of winning at all.</P><P>Rest is doable, just use your head...</P><P>Indoors you will loose against all melees.... no chance at all</P><P>Duelling is fun, Zek is even more *eg*</P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
