        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Actually playing a warrior who is experienced at fighting is hard, and almost impossible to kill post 50. They have great resists, tons of hp, and pets dont do much against em. Most also know how to dispell your dots when ya put em on with a simple dispell item. The only spells likely to be landed anyways are the lure based ones, and even those need to be reapplied if they dont get rid of em. And if they do manage to get you in hitting range or start dispelling you it can turn out badly.</P><P>Ndoro<BR>Vallon Zek<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
