        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I find that shadow step is an incredibly usfull duel spell, most people just dont know how to react. Its simple and confusing. Espcially when paired with a prenerf CoS. Since the spell effects look the same if you're out of their "hearing" radius they wont know you invised... hit and run with DoTs and lifetaps works on nearly any class. I've never lost a duel... though i dont think i've dueled more then 10 times... =P</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=94336"><BR><img src="http://crystaloracle.darktech.org/eqgrouping/images/beur/MakaSig.jpg" border=0><BR></a><BR><i>Click sig for Magelo Profile</i><BR><b> CHA has nothing to do with fear. Get over it</b><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
