         I think a well played magician is fairly hard with a right click shield of auras. They sirroco your pet so your's dies and you have epic beating on ya. They run out of range dispel dots and keep on reapplying rune. You don't win the mana game if they are conjuration spec with shield of auras. You can kill pet but they can just run and summon a new one.  </P><P>Monk's are hard. Can heal nicely with mend and do near rogue dmg without have to worry about backstabbing. </P><P>All hybrids are tough and paladins are near impossible to kill.</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Damodran on 05/22/2002  03:54:20<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
